comments: Luwawu-Cabarrot (ATL) places his forearm against LeVert (IND) and the contact is marginal during his shot attempt.
Turner (IND) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
LeVert (IND) places a hand on Luwawu-Cabarrot's (ATL) body and the contact is marginal during his jump shot attempt.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (ATL) makes contact to Sabonis's (IND) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hill (ATL) makes incidental contact with Brogdon's (IND) arm after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Duarte (IND) has his arms to Young's (ATL) sides as they engage, but he does not affect his FOM.
Collins (ATL) firms up in a screening position and the contact with Brogdon (IND) is marginal.
Sabonis (IND) makes contact to Collins' (ATL) head and affects his driving shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) cleanly blocks LeVert's (IND) driving shot attempt.
Collins (ATL) places two hands on Duarte (IND) during the pick but the contact is marginal.
Huerter (ATL) grabs Duarte's (IND) jersey as he elevates and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (IND) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
